intro
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to RuddyDoc.
This is a multi-line cue.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:10.000
RuddyDoc is a document parsing system
built on RDF and W3C standards.

section-overview
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:15.000
It supports multiple input formats:
Markdown, HTML, PDF, and more.

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:20.000
The parsed documents become queryable
knowledge graphs.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.000
SPARQL queries enable semantic search
across document collections.

NOTE Demonstrates a NOTE block which is a comment.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:32.000
Export formats include Markdown, HTML,
JSON, and RDF serializations.

conclusion
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Thank you for using RuddyDoc.
